.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\-\-audit\-log\-name=<AUDIT_LOG_FILE>
.sp
Full path and file name for the audit log file\&. Used by the
\fB\-\-file\-stats\fR
option, and the
\fIcopy\fR
command\&.
.RE
