Connection information for the first server in the format: <\fIuser\fR>[:<\fIpasswd\fR>]@<\fIhost\fR>[:<\fIport\fR>][:<\fIsocket\fR>] or <\fIlogin\-path\fR>[:<\fIport\fR>][:<\fIsocket\fR>]\&.
